flowchart TD
    A[Admin opens Email Notification menu] --> B[Choose one notification sub menu]
    B --> C[Load current template state]
    C --> D[Admin edits notification settings]
    D --> E[Click Save Changes]
    E --> F[Store template]

    F --> G{Business trigger occurs?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Load template by notification type]
    H --> I{Template enabled?}
    I -->|No| J[Skip sending]
    I -->|Yes| K[Render merge tags with real data]
    K --> L[Send admin and or user email]
    L --> M[Store email log]

    F --> N{Admin clicks Send Test?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Input test recipient]
    O --> P[Render template with sample data]
    P --> Q[Send test email]
    Q --> R[Store email log]